            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "`:set buftype?` will be `terminal`.\n\nYou shouldn't need numbers anymore. `:set relativenumber number` for the hybrid mode. \nSee http://jeffkreeftmeijer.com/2013/vims-new-hybrid-line-number-mode/\n",
